App-ZofCMS-Plugin-HTMLFactory-PageToBodyId

The module is a small plugin for L<App::ZofCMS>. Its purpose is to
automatically generate a value for an C<id=""> attribute that is to be
put on C<< <body> >> HTML element; this value would be used to
differentiate different pages on the site and is generated from
query C<dir> and C<page> parameters.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc App::ZofCMS::Plugin::HTMLFactory::PageToBodyId

